FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1784407673
OL,3,CMan charged over crash that killed
OL,4,CRaven, 24
OL,6,FFrancis Donaldson, 22, of Cardigan
OL,7,FDrive in Belfast, appeared before the
OL,8,Fcity's magistrates on Friday to face a
OL,9,Fnumber of charges, including causing
OL,10,Fdeath by dangerous driving on July 16.
OL,12,FDonaldson appeared upset in the dock
OL,13,Fas nine charges were read to him, and
OL,14,Fwas described in court as "fraught and
OL,15,Foverwrought".
OL,26,@vD@[OUwD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
