FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1784407673
OL,3,CMan charged over crash that killed
OL,4,CRaven, 24
OL,6,FHe replied yes when asked if he
OL,7,Funderstood the charges. The charges
OL,8,Falso include causing grievous bodily
OL,9,Fharm by dangerous driving and failing
OL,10,Fto stop at the scene of an accident. A
OL,11,Fpolice officer said he believed he
OL,12,Fcould connected the accused to the
OL,13,Fcharges.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
