OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1784407673
OL,3,CMan charged over crash that killed
OL,4,CRaven, 24
OL,6,FThe court heard Ms Adams and the man
OL,7,Fshe was with had been pedestrians, and
OL,8,Fdashcam footage shows the vehicle
OL,9,Fwhich struck them travelling at speed
OL,10,Fon the Limestone Road, running two red
OL,11,Flights before coming on to York
OL,12,FStreet, mounting the footpath on the
OL,13,Fopposite side of the road.
OL,15,FMs Adams was pronounced dead at the
OL,16,Fscene, while the man remains in
OL,17,Fhospital with injuries to his skull,
OL,18,Fneck, ribs, shoulder and knee. The
OL,19,Fdriver was captured on CCTV leaving
OL,20,Fthe scene on foot.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
