FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1784407673
OL,3,CMan charged over crash that killed
OL,4,CRaven, 24
OL,6,FThe court heard later the defendant's
OL,7,Fmother called police to say he had
OL,8,Fsent a message to his partner saying
OL,9,Fhe was "suicidal and was going to
OL,10,Fintentionally crash his car to kill
OL,11,Fhimself".
OL,13,FHe was found in the Cavehill area by
OL,14,Fpolice where the court heard he
OL,15,Fadmitted to being involved in the
OL,16,Fcrash, and asked police whether the
OL,17,Ftwo people were dead.
OL,26,@qD@HOUsD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1784407673
OL,3,CMan charged over crash that killed
OL,4,CRaven, 24
OL,6,FDuring police interview, the defendant
OL,7,Fprovided a statement saying he was the
OL,8,Fdriver of the vehicle, was responsible
OL,9,Ffor what happened, and was "having a
OL,10,Fmental health crisis".
OL,12,FHe also expressed remorse and
OL,13,Fcondolences to the families in a
OL,14,Fstatement that it was "never my
OL,15,Fintention to cause anyone harm except
OL,16,Fmyself".
OL,26,@qD@\OUrD@UO]vD@WOUxD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1784407673
OL,3,CMan charged over crash that killed
OL,4,CRaven, 24
OL,6,FHe added: "I accept I am responsible
OL,7,Ffor what happened. I was experiencing
OL,8,Fa mental health crisis both at the
OL,9,Ftime and in the immediate aftermath of
OL,10,Fthe collision.
OL,12,F"The police officer said they objected
OL,13,Fto bail "given the risk the defendant
OL,14,Fposes to himself and the wider
OL,15,Fcommunity", "community tensions", and
OL,16,Fsaid there is concern whether the
OL,17,Fdefendant could be "effectively
OL,18,Fmanaged on bail given his mental
OL,19,Fhealth issues".
OL,26,@nD@KOUtD@AO]uD@IOUwD@JO]wD@MOUwD@`O]yD@
OL,26,ATOU{D@NO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1784407673
OL,3,CMan charged over crash that killed
OL,4,CRaven, 24
OL,6,FA defence solicitor said the
OL,7,Fdefendant's family were present in
OL,8,Fcourt, and said they proposed bail
OL,9,Fwith conditions including going back
OL,10,Fto his home with two sureties from his
OL,11,Fmother and his aunt, and a package of
OL,12,Fsupport.
OL,14,FThe judge said he could see "the
OL,15,Fstate" the defendant is in, "crying
OL,16,Fand utterly remorseful", and refused
OL,17,Fto allow bail.
OL,26,@vD@]OUwD@FO]wD@]OUxD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1784407673
OL,3,CMan charged over crash that killed
OL,4,CRaven, 24
OL,6,F"Any issues in the community, that's
OL,7,Fwhat police are there for," he said "I
OL,8,Fcan't take someone in to protect
OL,9,Fthemselves, but there are two other
OL,10,Fissues that cause me some concern, one
OL,11,Fis considering what he did, I don't
OL,12,Fknow if this young man would try to do
OL,13,Fthe same again or something like it,
OL,14,Fand if he did, whether he would take
OL,15,Fsomeone with him.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@[O]oD@eOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1784407673
OL,3,CMan charged over crash that killed
OL,4,CRaven, 24
OL,6,F"He also left the scene. I think the
OL,7,Fpolice are not unreasonable in saying
OL,8,Fthey fear that bail could not be
OL,9,Fadequately managed due to all the
OL,10,Fcircumstances, including his mental
OL,11,Fhealth.
OL,13,F"Unless you could persuade a court
OL,14,Fthat there were sufficient safeguards
OL,15,Fto overcome the issues that I have
OL,16,Fraised with you, bail has to be
OL,17,Frefused at this stage."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUyD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/10
